<P>
OAKLAND A'S (BASEBALL TEAM); BOSTON RED SOX (BASEBALL TEAM); BASEBALL 
CHAMPIONSHIPS; AMERICAN LEAGUE (BASEBALL); STEWART, DAVE; CLEMENS, ROGER 
</P>
