Pirates' Jeff King at second base. ; Photo, Taking a seat -- Andy Van Slyke of 
Pittsburgh falls to the ground while at bat and later was thrown out trying to 
advance from second to third on a fly to right field Friday in the second game 
of the National League championship series. United Press International; Photo, 
