<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ORION PICTURES CORP; METROMEDIA CO; KLUGE, JOHN; MOTION PICTURE INDUSTRY -- 
FINANCES 
