<P>
NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- BRAZIL; PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT; TECHNOLOGY; COLLOR DE MELLO, 
FERNANDO; BRAZIL -- ARMED FORCES; PLUTONIUM; NUCLEAR REACTORS 
</P>
